          <w:lang w:val="en-GB"/>
        </w:rPr>
        <w:t>Automated GDPR Compliance: A Data Discovery Concept for Bosch</w:t>
      <w:br/></w:r>
      
      <w:r>
        <w:rPr>
          <w:b/>
          <w:bCs/>
          <w:lang w:val="en-GB"/>
        </w:rPr>
        <w:t>Concept Paper for the Identification and Categorization of Personal Data on Corporate Drives and SharePoint Sites</w:t>
      </w:r>
    </w:p>
    <w:p w14:paraId="161245AB" w14:textId="60E6B7C8" w:rsidR="00153B69" w:rsidRPr="00153B69" w:rsidRDefault="00153B69" w:rsidP="00153B69">
      <w:pPr>
        <w:rPr>
          <w:b/>
          <w:bCs/>
          <w:lang w:val="en-GB"/>
        </w:rPr>
      </w:pPr>
      <w:r>
        <w:rPr>
          <w:rFonts w:asciiTheme="majorHAnsi" w:eastAsia="Times New Roman" w:hAnsiTheme="majorHAnsi" w:cstheme="majorBidi"/>
          <w:color w:val="0F4761" w:themeColor="accent1" w:themeShade="BF"/>
          <w:sz w:val="32"/>
          <w:szCs w:val="32"/>
          <w:lang w:val="en-GB"/>
        </w:rPr>
        <w:t>Introduction: Objective and Background</w:t>
      </w:r>
    </w:p>
    <w:p w14:paraId="5607735B" w14:textId="37FE61DA" w:rsidR="00153B69" w:rsidRDefault="00153B69" w:rsidP="00153B69">
      <w:pPr>
        <w:rPr>
          <w:lang w:val="en-GB"/>
        </w:rPr>
      </w:pPr>
      <w:r>
        <w:rPr>
          <w:lang w:val="en-GB"/>
        </w:rPr>
        <w:t>As part of a 48-hour hackathon, an innovative software concept is being developed to enable the automated identification and categorization of personal and GDPR-relevant data on corporate drives, SharePoint sites, OneDrives, and other data sources. The goal is to sustainably identify sensible data and delete it when required. The solution will be developed as a prototype (Proof of Concept) and serve as a basis for future scaling.</w:t>
      </w:r>
      
      
      
      
      
      
    </w:p>
    <w:p w14:paraId="7D63C8F3" w14:textId="77777777" w:rsidR="00823C55" w:rsidRDefault="00823C55" w:rsidP="00823C55">
      <w:pPr>
        <w:rPr>
          <w:lang w:val="en-GB"/>
        </w:rPr>
      </w:pPr>
      <w:r>
        <w:rPr>
          <w:rFonts w:asciiTheme="majorHAnsi" w:eastAsia="Times New Roman" w:hAnsiTheme="majorHAnsi" w:cstheme="majorBidi"/>
          <w:color w:val="0F4761" w:themeColor="accent1" w:themeShade="BF"/>
          <w:sz w:val="32"/>
          <w:szCs w:val="32"/>
          <w:lang w:val="en-GB"/>
        </w:rPr>
        <w:t>Legal Basis:</w:t>
      </w:r>
    </w:p>
    <w:p w14:paraId="668D1E11" w14:textId="2960B09A" w:rsidR="00823C55" w:rsidRPr="00823C55" w:rsidRDefault="00823C55" w:rsidP="00823C55">
      <w:pPr>
        <w:rPr>
          <w:lang w:val="en-GB"/>
        </w:rPr>
      </w:pPr>
      <w:r>
        <w:rPr>
          <w:lang w:val="en-GB"/>
        </w:rPr>
        <w:t>The General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR) is a comprehensive data privacy law enacted by the European Union (EU). It regulates how organizations worldwide must handle the personal data of individuals located in the EU. The primary goal is to give individuals control over their personal data and to unify data privacy and security laws across Europe.</w:t>
      </w:r>
    </w:p>
    <w:p w14:paraId="58376647" w14:textId="297B1716" w:rsidR="00823C55" w:rsidRPr="00823C55" w:rsidRDefault="00823C55" w:rsidP="00823C55">
      <w:r>
        <w:t>Relevant Articles:</w:t>
      </w:r>
      
      
      
      
    </w:p>
