          <w:lang w:val="en-GB"/>
        </w:rPr>
        <w:t>With the introduction of the General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR), companies are obligated to manage personal data transparently and delete it after the retention period is exceeded. In large organizations like Bosch, the multitude and distribution of data sources, approximately 300,000 OneDrives and globally distributed shared drives and SharePoint sites, pose a significant challenge. Manual auditing is hardly feasible, creating a high demand for automated tools that can reliably identify and classify data relevant to data protection.</w:t>
      </w:r>
      
      
      
      
      
      
      
      
      
      
    </w:p>
    <w:p w14:paraId="6ABE72AE" w14:textId="43A7A928" w:rsidR="00153B69" w:rsidRPr="00153B69" w:rsidRDefault="00153B69" w:rsidP="00153B69">
      <w:pPr>
        <w:rPr>
          <w:rFonts w:asciiTheme="majorHAnsi" w:eastAsia="Times New Roman" w:hAnsiTheme="majorHAnsi" w:cstheme="majorBidi"/>
          <w:color w:val="0F4761" w:themeColor="accent1" w:themeShade="BF"/>
          <w:sz w:val="32"/>
          <w:szCs w:val="32"/>
          <w:lang w:val="en-GB"/>
        </w:rPr>
      </w:pPr>
      <w:r>
        <w:rPr>
          <w:rFonts w:asciiTheme="majorHAnsi" w:eastAsia="Times New Roman" w:hAnsiTheme="majorHAnsi" w:cstheme="majorBidi"/>
          <w:color w:val="0F4761" w:themeColor="accent1" w:themeShade="BF"/>
          <w:sz w:val="32"/>
          <w:szCs w:val="32"/>
          <w:lang w:val="en-GB"/>
        </w:rPr>
        <w:t>Solution Approach: Software Concept and AI Implementation</w:t>
      </w:r>
    </w:p>
    <w:p w14:paraId="27427A0B" w14:textId="647E25E9" w:rsidR="00153B69" w:rsidRDefault="00153B69" w:rsidP="00153B69">
      <w:pPr>
        <w:rPr>
          <w:lang w:val="en-GB"/>
        </w:rPr>
      </w:pPr>
      <w:r>
        <w:rPr>
          <w:lang w:val="en-GB"/>
        </w:rPr>
        <w:t>The planned software combines modern AI technologies with classic search mechanisms to detect personal and sensitive data across various corporate databases. The scan will be conducted in two stages: first, a complete search (full scan) is performed, followed by subsequent checks at regular intervals that only review files modified since the last scan (delta scan). The AI will provide suggestions for data categorization, with the final review and deletion of the file being conducted by a human to ensure compliance. The discovered data can always be attributed to a person, either as a direct owner (e.g., OneDrive) or indirectly as a &quot;Master of Data&quot; (e.g., SharePoint, Shared Drives).</w:t>
      </w:r>
      
      
      
      
    </w:p>
